<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR5c0057-zh-25e9857f" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>老子註譯及評介</title><editor role="translator">Chen Guying 陳鼓應</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="4">The copyright status of this work is unclear</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>老子註譯及評介</title>北京：中華書局，1994</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR5c0057"><title xml:lang="och">老子</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="zh">Chinese</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2023-10-31T08:32:05.651+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR5c0057-start"><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T18:28:27.226+09:00">道是独立无偶的，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T18:28:53.541+09:00">浑沌未分的统一体产生天地，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T18:29:17.391+09:00">天地产生阴阳之气，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T18:29:33.672+09:00">阴阳两气相交而形成各种新生体。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T18:29:55.811+09:00">万物背阴</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T18:30:10.239+09:00">而向阳，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-14T18:30:20.765+09:00">阴阳两气互相激荡而成新的和谐体。</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>